          "bbox": [60, 40, 430, 100],
          "text": "LOCAL BUDGET TALKS RESUME"
        },
        {
          "id": "paragraph-left-1",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "bbox": [60, 112, 430, 192],
          "text": "City officials returned to budget negotiations after late night committee meetings."
        },
        {
          "id": "paragraph-left-2",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "bbox": [60, 204, 430, 292],
          "text": "Negotiators say transit, housing, and school maintenance remain the biggest unresolved items."
        },
        {
          "id": "headline-right-1",
          "type": "headline",
          "bbox": [540, 60, 930, 120],
          "text": "HARBOR PROJECT MOVES AHEAD"
        },
        {
          "id": "paragraph-right-1",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "bbox": [540, 132, 930, 214],
          "text": "A revised construction plan cleared review, allowing the shoreline reinforcement program to begin."
        },
        {
          "id": "image-right-1",
          "type": "image",
          "bbox": [550, 224, 920, 404]
        },
        {
          "id": "caption-right-1",
          "type": "caption",
          "bbox": [550, 410, 920, 446],
          "text": "Crews survey the eastern breakwater before heavy equipment arrives."
        },
        {
          "id": "paragraph-right-2",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "bbox": [540, 458, 930, 562],
          "text": "Engineers expect the first stabilization phase to finish before the summer storm season."
        },
        {
          "id": "headline-left-2",
          "type": "headline",
          "bbox": [60, 344, 430, 404],
          "text": "SCHOOL BOARD DELAYS VOTE"
        },
        {
          "id": "paragraph-left-3",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "bbox": [60, 416, 430, 502],
          "text": "Members postponed the curriculum vote after parents requested more public comment sessions."
        },
        {
          "id": "paragraph-left-4",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "bbox": [60, 514, 430, 606],
          "text": "A revised calendar now includes two hearings and a written feedback period for educators."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
